\fs32 \cf0 Areas we have compromised:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What we wear\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What we wear is debatably becoming more and more risqu\'e9 but there is one area where there is in my mind a clear disconnect.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}bathing suits\'85more specifically bikini\'92s.  \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1
\f3 \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When Louis R\'e9ard was unable to convince Parisian models to wear what we now consider to be a modern-day bikini, nineteen-year-old Micheline Bernardini stepped up to the plate and became the first to ever pose in the swimwear.\'a0\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1
\f4\b \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The Disconnect:  Dad/Husband who wouldn\'92t let their daughter/wife outside in their underwear but ok with a bikini!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1
\f3\b0 \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are women who would be mortified if you saw them in their underwear but will happily walk outside onto a beach in the same amount of fabric in front of others\'85and be proud sometimes.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are some who say it has to do with the situation though\'85it\'92s a pool or a beach\'85ok\'85so same question:\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl2\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If your wife/daughter came to you and said they were going to the beach / pool in the underwear\'85how do you feel about that?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is no verse for the line in scripture for this and I don\'92t think there really should be one actually.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What we listen to:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
